Automation of software quality assurance is key to DevOps success. We present how automated performance benchmarks may be included into continuous integration. As an example, we report on regression benchmarks for application monitoring frameworks and illustrate the inclusion of automated benchmarks into continuous integration setups.</p>  <p>This dataset supplements the paper and contains the raw experimental data for each experiment.</p></subfield>   </datafield>   <datafield tag="909" ind1="C" ind2="4">     <subfield code="y">2015</subfield>
